title: Mayor Taron Margaryan met with his colleague from Antony (Yerevan Municipality)
text: ( Source : Yerevan Municipality ) 09.10. 2015 At the behest of Yerevan Mayor the delegation headed by the Mayor of Antony, France Jean-Yves Senant arrived in Yerevan to participate in 'Erebuni-Yerevan 2797' celebration and met with Mayor Taron
